Direct Known Subclasses:
AttributeDenotation, CheckedSequence
public class Sequence
extends Vector
implements Serializable

A Sequence is just a collection of things in G2. It is implemented by subclassing Vector. Use the methods in that class to access and set elements. In the not so distant future, we might add more G2 sequence like operations, such as remove-last, etc.

See Also:
Vector, Serialized Form
